---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar";
import Heading from "../components/foundations/Heading";
import BodyText from "../components/foundations/BodyText";

const title = "Activités - Académie Stéphanoise";
const description =
  "En savoir plus sur l'Académie Stéphanoise, un lieu dédié aux arts martiaux et au fitness à Saint-Étienne.";
const keywords =
  "Académie Stéphanoise, arts martiaux, fitness, Saint-Étienne, activités";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} keywords={keywords}>
  <Navbar />
  <div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto pt-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
      <Heading level={2}> La liste de nos activités </Heading>
      <BodyText variant="headline" className="mt-4">
        Découvrez nos activités sportives et de remise en forme.
      </BodyText>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-neutral-900 mt-20 py-8 sm:py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div
        class="-mx-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-0.5 overflow-hidden sm:mx-0 sm:rounded-2xl md:grid-cols-3"
      >
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 justify-center items-center flex flex-col space-y-4 p-4 sm:p-6 hover:bg-neutral-700 transition ease-out-300 cursor-pointer">
          <img
            class="max-h-12 w-fit object-contain rounded-full bg-orange-100"
            src="/assets/icons/boxe_picto.png"
            alt="Boxe"
            width="158"
            height="48"
          />
          <Heading level={4} white>
            Boxe pieds-poings
          </Heading>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 justify-center items-center flex flex-col space-y-4 p-4 sm:p-6 hover:bg-neutral-700 transition ease-out-300 cursor-pointer">
          <img
            class="max-h-12 w-fit object-contain rounded-full bg-yellow-100"
            src="/assets/icons/crosstraining_picto.png"
            alt="Cross Training"
            width="158"
            height="48"
          />
          <Heading level={4} white>
            Cross Training
          </Heading>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 justify-center items-center flex flex-col space-y-4 p-4 sm:p-6 hover:bg-neutral-700 transition ease-out-300 cursor-pointer">
          <img
            class="max-h-12 w-fit object-contain rounded-full bg-blue-100"
            src="/assets/icons/krav_picto.png"
            alt="Krav Maga"
            width="158"
            height="48"
          />
          <Heading level={4} white>
            Krav Maga
          </Heading>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 justify-center items-center flex flex-col space-y-4 p-4 sm:p-6 hover:bg-neutral-700 transition ease-out-300 cursor-pointer">
          <img
            class="max-h-12 w-fit object-contain rounded-full bg-red-100"
            src="/assets/icons/lutalivre_picto.png"
            alt="Luta Livre"
            width="158"
            height="48"
          />
          <Heading level={4} white>
            Luta Livre
          </Heading>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 justify-center items-center flex flex-col space-y-4 p-4 sm:p-6 hover:bg-neutral-700 transition ease-out-300 cursor-pointer">
          <img
            class="max-h-12 w-fit object-contain rounded-full bg-green-100"
            src="/assets/icons/mma_picto.png"
            alt="MMA"
            width="158"
            height="48"
          />
          <Heading level={4} white>
            MMA
          </Heading>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 justify-center items-center flex flex-col space-y-4 p-4 sm:p-6 hover:bg-neutral-700 transition ease-out-300 cursor-pointer">
          <img
            class="max-h-12 w-fit object-contain rounded-full bg-purple-100"
            src="/assets/icons/tolpar_picto.png"
            alt="Tolpar"
            width="158"
            height="48"
          />
          <Heading level={4} white>
            Tolpar
          </Heading>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div>
          <Heading level={3}>Boxe pieds poing</Heading>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-700">
            Cours de boxe dynamique et technique, conçu pour améliorer la forme physique générale, la coordination et la confiance en soi. Idéal pour ceux qui souhaitent apprendre les bases.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Niveau:</strong> Intermédiaire</li>
            <li><strong>Durée:</strong> 1 heure</li>
            <li><strong>Horaires:</strong> Plusieurs fois par semaine</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-md"
            src="/assets/icons/boxe_picto.png"
            alt="Boxe pieds poing"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
